<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1050732' id='t-1050732'>there are some very small, cute but bad cats.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:46
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1055561' id='t-1055561'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1057205' id='t-1057205'>SOPA, PIPA, ACTA, TPP and ITU.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1063943' id='t-1063943'>And also, like Facebook and Google, they claim they are friends of the mouse,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1069298' id='t-1069298'>but sometimes we see them dating the cats.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1073485' id='t-1073485'>So my conclusion is very simple.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1076669' id='t-1076669'>We Chinese fight for our freedom,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1079514' id='t-1079514'>you just watch your bad cats.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1083109' id='t-1083109'>Don't let them hook [up] with the Chinese cats.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1086012' id='t-1086012'>Only in this way, in the future,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1088853' id='t-1088853'>we will achieve the dreams of the mouse:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1092101' id='t-1092101'>that we can tweet anytime, anywhere, without fear.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
